This is a placeholder for FAQ No communication to PMAC.pdf. To properly process PDFs, you need either:
1. A valid Unstructured.io API key (sign up at https://unstructured.io)
2. Install and use a local PDF parsing library like pdf-parse

To get an Unstructured API key:
- Visit https://unstructured.io/developers
- Sign up for a free account
- Get your API key from the dashboard
- Set it using: encore secret set --type local UnstructuredApiKey YOUR_KEY_HERE
